<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Application Status Update</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f2f5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
    .email-header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .email-header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
    .email-body {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #34495e;
    }
    .email-body p {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .reason-box {
      background-color: #fff4f4;
      border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }
    .reason-box strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #c0392b;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #95a5a6;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Application Status Update</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Dear <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for taking the time to apply for the <strong>{{jobTitle}}</strong> role at <strong>{{companyName}}</strong>. We genuinely appreciate your interest in joining our team.</p>
      <p>After careful review and consideration, we regret to inform you that we will not be moving forward with your application at this time.</p>

      {{#if reason}}
      <div class="reason-box">
        <strong>Feedback:</strong>
        <p>{{reason}}</p>
      </div>
      {{/if}}

      <p>Please don't be discouragedâ€”your qualifications are impressive, and we encourage you to explore future opportunities with us as they arise.</p>
      <p>We wish you all the best in your job search and professional journey.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2025 {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
